dataset_description.json.Name: Top-down attention impacts neural dynamics during narratives with overlapping event scripts

README:
This dataset contains fMRI data from:

A. De Soares, T. Kim, F. Mugisho, E. Zhu, A. Lin, C. Zheng, C. Baldassano. "Top-down attention impacts neural dynamics during narratives with overlapping event scripts."

Stimuli are available here: https://figshare.com/projects/Script_Combination_Stories/168656

Note: run 2 for sub-14 was interrupted, so the final two stories were presented in a third run.
